Quality of life encompasses a personâ€™s overall sense of well-being, which includes physical health, mental health, and emotional stability. It reflects how individuals perceive their position in life in the context of their goals, expectations, and concerns.
It involves the degree of satisfaction or dissatisfaction with various aspects of life, such as personal relationships, work, leisure activities, and daily living conditions. High quality of life is typically associated with high levels of contentment and happiness.
